cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.CC

This paper deals with updating databases and knowledge bases, which falls under the category of databases (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also involves logic and reasoning, which are covered by the categories of logic in computer science (cs.LO) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper discusses techniques for efficient query answering and integrity checking, which could fall under the category of computational complexity (cs.CC).
